erts](/expertises/power-platform) en [Azure-engineers](/expertises/azure) om het meeste uit jouw Microsoft 365 omgeving te halen. Hierdoor is het bij ShareValue mogelijk om een totaaloplossing voor jouw bedrijf te vinden die op al jouw Microsoft 365 wensen aansluit.",{"id":459,"name":460,"alternativeText":19,"caption":19,"width":20,"height":212,"formats":461,"hash":482,"ext":24,"mime":27,"size":483,"url":484,"previewUrl":19,"provider":55,"provider_metadata":19,"createdAt":485,"updatedAt":485,"documentId":486,"publishedAt":58,"focalPoint":19},789,"teamwork.jpg",{"large":462,"small":467,"medium":472,"thumbnail":477},{"ext":24,"url":463,"hash":464,"mime":27,"name":465,"path":19,"size":466,"width":30,"height":219},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/large_teamwork_8f4a7b0c14.jpg","large_teamwork_8f4a7b0c14","large_teamwork.jpg",80.4,{"ext":24,"url":468,"hash":469,"mime":27,"name":470,"path":19,"size":471,"width":21,"height":225},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/small_teamwork_8f4a7b0c14.jpg","small_teamwork_8f4a7b0c14","small_teamwork.jpg",27.14,{"ext":24,"url":473,"hash":474,"mime":27,"name":475,"path":19,"size":476,"width":43,"height":231},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/medium_teamwork_8f4a7b0c14.jpg","medium_teamwork_8f4a7b0c14","medium_teamwork.jpg",51.59,{"ext":24,"url":478,"hash":479,"mime":27,"name":480,"path":19,"size":481,"width":237,"height":78},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_teamwork_8f4a7b0c14.jpg","thumbnail_teamwork_8f4a7b0c14","thumbnail_teamwork.jpg",8.11,"teamwork_8f4a7b0c14",116.53,"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/teamwork_8f4a7b0c14.jpg","2024-08-08T10:07:23.468Z","uo85gvimf7llsbaoahqw08m3",{"id":488,"title":489,"callToActionText":490,"callToActionLinkUrl":491,"body":19,"imageUrl":492,"__component":493},48,"Wil je weten wat onze collega's allemaal kunnen?","Lees de klantcase over ons werk bij Groeneveld-BEKA","/klantcases/gesme